@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_yklbbp(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.abs(v1)
    tmp = ((0.52 / (tmp + 0.99 / tmp + 0.22)) + wp.sin(v2))
    v1 = (0.22 + tmp)
    v1 = wp.abs(tmp)
    v0 = v2
    data[tid] = v0
